snippet.title: Pizza Morgana Trailer 1
snippet.description:
Corbomite Games brings you the charming tale of a young girl who is accidentally teleported into a magical dimension filled with monsters, vampires, faeries, and daemons, which all just happen to be employed as pizza delivery guys. And, of course they work for an arch wizard (and chef), named Morgan!

Coming August 16th!
